            <td valign="top">66</td>
            <td valign="top">8/15 patients with IMID and risk factors for TB infection were positive to TST, T-SPOT.<italic>TB</italic> and QFT-IT. The remaining 7 were negative to TST but positive to either T-SPOT.<italic>TB</italic> and/or QFT-IT. 35/51 patients with IMID without risk factors for TB infection were negative to TST, T-SPOT.<italic>TB</italic> and QFT-IT.</td>
