            <td rowspan="3" valign="top">T-SPOT.<italic>TB</italic></td>
            <td rowspan="3" valign="top">70</td>
            <td valign="top">Agreement between TST and T-SPOT.<italic>TB</italic> results was moderate (72.8%)</td>
